lass="note note-primary">测试标签1</p><p class="note note-secondary">测试标签2</p><p class="note note-danger">测试标签3</p><p class="note note-warning">测试标签4</p><p class="note note-info">测试标签5</p><p class="note note-light">测试标签6</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
